result.name: 2005-english-nature-the-dee-estuary-biotope-survey
result.notes: A Natural England commissioned survey conducted by the Institute of Estuarine and Coastal Studies (IECS). The survey aimed to standardise fauna, and the information for mud/sand habitats and communities of the Dee Esturay SAC, in order to act as a baseline for future management and condition monitoring. Phase I survey of the intertidal zone, mud/sand and rock habitats resulting in the production of detailed biotope maps.
result.title: 2005 English Nature The Dee Estuary Biotope Survey
